<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>Q&A -
        <%=item.title%>
    </title>
    <link href="css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="http://localhost:3000/css/App.css">
    <style>
        @import "https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Noto+Sans?fbclid=IwAR1rho8MwXOMwknTk84vc0Y-y2PKP0Q5ce5guoQWm1to61Yy9tdqqUuHbyQ";
        body {
            font-family: NotoSansCJKkr-light;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <% include ./header %>
    </header>
    <section class="background1_2">
        <br><br><br><br>
        <div class="QA_title">Q&A</div><br><br>
        <div class="intro">
            앱앤미와 관련되어 궁금한 점이 있다면<br> 질문하고 궁금증을 풀어보세요. </div><br><br><br>
        <hr width="80%" color="gray" size="1"><br><br><br><br>

        <table width="1000px" class="list-table" align=center frame=void style='border-left:0;border-right:0;border-bottom:0;border-top:0'>
            <tr height="40px">
                <td bgcolor=#f6f6f6>제목</td>
                <td bgcolor=#fbfbfb size="35" style="margin-left:0%; text-align: left">
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <%=item.title%>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr height="40px">
                <td bgcolor=#f6f6f6>작성자</td>
                <td bgcolor=#fbfbfb size="35" style=" margin-left:0%; text-align: left">
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <%=item.name%>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr height="40px">
                <td colspan="2" style=" padding:20px 35px; text-align: left; height: 500px; vertical-align: top;">
                    <%=item.content%>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <img style="float: right; margin-right:13%; margin-top:1.5%;" src="http://localhost:3000/img/list.jpg">

    </section>
    <footer>
        <% include ./footer %>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>
</body>

</html>